sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Controller
    participant Service
    participant Repository
    participant DB

    Browser->>Controller: POST /todos (form data)
    Controller->>Service: createTodo(dto)
    Service->>Repository: save(todoEntity)
    Repository->>DB: INSERT todo
    DB-->>Repository: OK (id)
    Repository-->>Service: savedEntity
    Service-->>Controller: result/redirect
    Controller-->>Browser: 302 Redirect -> /todos/{id} or /todos

    Note over Controller,Service: validation (title required) before save
